global_rules.code_system: Information needed - research plate type code system
global_rules.character_restrictions: Uses both O and 0 - O with letters, 0 with numbers; Full rules: Follow the syntax pattern.  The letter 'O' is blocky and the number '0' is more oblong.  Key all verticals except "TRUCK" & "ARK" as seen Vertical characters must be entered as seen.

stacked_characters.position: Y - OMIT ARK verticals on left side of plate.; Y - Verticals on right are NOT keyed.
stacked_characters.notes: Include military/service codes, omit vehicle type; Extracted from 6 plate types with character modifications
